data.description: Come and see this very special 3 Bedroom/2.5 Bath Seaside End Townhome with 2-Car Garage, all ready with beautiful features for move-in. This end-unit provides so much extra privacy for you! ***SPECIAL FEATURES INCLUDE: Kitchen Equipped with: Quartz Countertops, Stainless Appliances, Closet Panty, Pull-out pantry drawers, Upgraded Chandelier, Under Mount Single Basin Sink.  Primary Suite has 2 Walk-In Closets and an Ensuite Bath with Dual Sink Vanity and Walk-In Shower,   Oversized 2nd and 3rd Bedrooms and second Bathroom,   Powder Room Downstairs for Guests,   Plank Tile Floors on 1st Floor,   Epoxy Garage Floor and Overhead Racks, and  Screened-in Lanai with Kickplate.  ***HOA COVERS: Lawn Maintenance, Community Pool, Fitness Center, Playground, Clubhouse, Power Washing, Pond Management.  ***LOCATION: Centrally located. Just around the corner are A+ schools, Gullett Elementary, Lakewood Ranch High School, and Mona Jain Middle School, LECOM, & Manatee Tech East Campus. Minutes to shopping, restaurants, gyms, salons, bars, etc. Minutes to Lakewood Ranch Downtown, Waterside, Downtown Sarasota, SRQ International Airport, the top rated beaches in the country, and UTC Shopping.
